        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.2</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2026 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>What's New in 1.1.2</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Download &amp; Install and Download Only buttons — save the installer to Downloads without running it</li>
                    <li>Download Only success banner with Reveal in Finder button</li>
                    <li>Favourites — star up to 5 products; favourites float to the top with animation</li>
                    <li>Click outside the product detail sheet to close it</li>
                    <li>Blackmagic Cintel added (replaces Duplicator)</li>
                    <li>Blackmagic RAW shows info banner explaining it is bundled with Camera Setup</li>
                    <li>Products sorted A–Z with favourites pinned first</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
